{"tid":2140840,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"首案被告稱變相迫認罪申人身保護令 律政司指概念上非禁保釋","createTime":"2020-08-05T09:09:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T12:34:46.000Z","uid":56115,"like":41,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"586d2a6955449dd546957d7fd33408f77bffa8de","tid":2140840,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:09:52.000Z","msg":"唐英傑今由資深大律師戴啟思代表<br />\n<br />\n申請方質疑，條文列明除非法庭有充分理由相信被告「不會繼續」實施危害國家安全行為，否則不能批准保釋，<span class=\"red\">變相要求被告先承認自己干犯國安罪行</span>，違反《普通法》的無罪推定原則，有違現有保釋法律。<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，亦指由於處理提堂的總裁判官蘇惠德是行政長官委任的指定法官，就算他本人處事公正，也不符合司法人員須具備獨立性的憲制要求，因此無資格在本案行使香港特區的司法權力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200805/YTCEXNTCC4IGB5TZRQQJCD3ACI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200805%2FYTCEXNTCC4IGB5TZRQQJCD3ACI%2F&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7ZeavaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=3361e86a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200805%2FYTCEXNTCC4IGB5TZRQQJCD3ACI%2F&h=3bec111e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200805/YTCEXNTCC4IGB5TZRQQJCD3ACI/</a>"},{"pid":"8c3a421d37b9d50f1c7aa6b4e7db3c8beb7feee8","tid":2140840,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:11:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b691c5eb8af908cc397bbfd90119d1d97ed55a","tid":2140840,"uid":362492,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:13:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2df1933974d94434e7eb7e5403c240aa5daefd03","tid":2140840,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:16:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1759fc6b1baeb48f86894d4e1ef94d9925733489","tid":2140840,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:17:07.000Z","msg":"電單車手足人身保護令狀及保釋申請 押後至8月20日1030於高等法院判法院第一庭聆訊<br />\